<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>泽尔集团 · Zell Group</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,600;14..32,700;14..32,800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        /* ===== 全局重置 ===== */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --color-black: #0a0a0a;
            --color-red: #c42e2e;
            --color-red-dark: #8a1f1f;
            --color-white: #f0efed;
            --color-gray: #8a8a8a;
            --color-light-gray: #d4d4d4;
            --font-sans: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--color-black);
            color: var(--color-white);
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.5;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* ===== 通用容器 ===== */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2.5rem;
        }

        /* ===== 顶部导航 (建构主义风格) ===== */
        .navbar {
            padding: 1.2rem 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-red);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .navbar::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -6px;
            left: 0;
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--color-red);
        }
        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--color-white);
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .navbar .logo .red {
            color: var(--color-red);
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--color-light-gray);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            position: relative;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--color-white);
        }
        .nav-links a.active {
            color: var(--color-red);
        }
        .nav-links a.active::before {
            content: '◆ ';
            font-size: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--color-red);
        }

        /* ===== Hero 区域 (激进构图) ===== */
        .hero {
            padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-red);
            position: relative;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: start;
        }
        /* 红色斜角装饰块 */
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: var(--color-red);
            clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 0 0, 100% 100%);
            opacity: 0.15;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero-left h1 {
            font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 0.95;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .hero-left h1 .red {
            color: var(--color-red);
        }
        .hero-left .subhead {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--color-gray);
            font-weight: 300;
            max-width: 420px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--color-red);
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
        }
        .hero-right {
            text-align: right;
            align-self: end;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .hero-right .year {
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--color-red);
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        }
        .hero-right .meta {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--color-gray);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-top: 0.2rem;
        }
        .hero-right .meta span {
            display: block;
            color: var(--color-light-gray);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ===== 建构主义装饰线 ===== */
        .construct-line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--color-red);
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .construct-line::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: -4px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 10px;
            background: var(--color-black);
            border: 2px solid var(--color-red);
            border-top: none;
        }

        /* ===== 使命愿景 (双栏) ===== */
        .mission-section {
            padding: 3.5rem 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.3);
        }
        .mission-item .label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--color-red);
            font-weight: 700;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .mission-item h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .mission-item p {
            color: var(--color-gray);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* ===== 三大板块 (网格) ===== */
        .divisions-section {
            padding: 3.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.3);
        }
        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-red);
            padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }
        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }
        .section-header .number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--color-red);
            line-height: 1;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        .divisions-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .division-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.3);
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.02);
        }
        .division-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--color-red);
            background: rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.06);
        }
        .division-card .number-mark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0.5rem;
            right: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.08);
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .division-card .icon {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--color-red);
        }
        .division-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }
        .division-card .sub {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: var(--color-gray);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }
        .division-card p {
            color: var(--color-gray);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* ===== 数据统计 (粗体数字) ===== */
        .stats-section {
            padding: 3.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.3);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-item .number {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--color-red);
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .stat-item .label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            color: var(--color-gray);
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
        }

        /* ===== 新闻动态 ===== */
        .news-section {
            padding: 3.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.3);
        }
        .news-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .news-item {
            padding: 1.2rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.2);
        }
        .news-item .date {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--color-red);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .news-item h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin: 0.3rem 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .news-item p {
            color: var(--color-gray);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* ===== 页脚 ===== */
        .footer {
            padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .footer-brand h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }
        .footer-brand h3 .red {
            color: var(--color-red);
        }
        .footer-brand p {
            color: var(--color-gray);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            max-width: 260px;
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
        }
        .footer-col h4 {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--color-red);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }
        .footer-col a {
            display: block;
            color: var(--color-gray);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .footer-col a:hover {
            color: var(--color-white);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--color-gray);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(196, 46, 46, 0.2);
        }
        .footer-bottom a {
            color: var(--color-gray);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .footer-bottom a:hover {
            color: var(--color-white);
        }

        /* ===== 响应式 ===== */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .container { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
            .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
            .hero-right { text-align: left; align-self: start; }
            .hero-right .year { font-size: 3.5rem; }
            .mission-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
            .divisions-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .stats-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .news-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .navbar { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
            .nav-links { gap: 1.2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
            .stats-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .footer-bottom a { margin: 0 0.5rem; }
            .hero-left h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- ===== 导航栏 ===== -->
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar">
            <a href="/Zell.html" class="logo">泽尔<span class="red">·</span>集团</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="#mission" class="active">理念</a>
                <a href="#divisions">业务</a>
                <a href="#news">动态</a>
                <a href="/gate.html">Gate</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== Hero ===== -->
    <div class="container">
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-left">
                <h1>
                    构建<br />
                    <span class="red">科技</span>与<br />
                    自然共生
                </h1>
                <div class="subhead">
                    泽尔集团 · 以人文精神驱动的科技企业。<br />
                    创新，源于对自然法则的深刻理解。
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-right">
                <div class="year">2024</div>
                <div class="meta">
                    成立于 <span>上海 · 中国</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 建构主义装饰线 ===== -->
    <div class="construct-line"></div>

    <!-- ===== 使命与愿景 ===== -->
    <div class="container">
        <section class="mission-section" id="mission">
            <div class="mission-item">
                <span class="label">◆ 使命</span>
                <h2>科技回归<br />服务本质</h2>
                <p>
                    将尖端技术融入人类生活的自然脉络中，创造有温度、可持续、尊重个体尊严的产品与解决方案。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-item">
                <span class="label">◆ 愿景</span>
                <h2>数字时代的<br />自然主义者</h2>
                <p>
                    在效率与诗意之间寻找平衡，构建技术与人文和谐共生的未来生态。这是我们的哲学承诺。
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 三大业务板块 ===== -->
    <div class="container">
        <section class="divisions-section" id="divisions">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>核心业务</h2>
                <span class="number">03</span>
            </div>
            <div class="divisions-grid">
                <div class="division-card">
                    <span class="number-mark">01</span>
                    <span class="icon">📜</span>
                    <h3>泽尔文化</h3>
                    <span class="sub">Zell Culture</span>
                    <p>以叙事为纽带，构建跨媒体内容生态。从世界观到沉浸体验，让文化连接心灵。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="division-card">
                    <span class="number-mark">02</span>
                    <span class="icon">⚡</span>
                    <h3>泽尔电子</h3>
                    <span class="sub">Zell Electronics</span>
                    <p>探索人机共生新边界。极简设计、直觉交互、可持续材料，重新定义电子产品价值。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="division-card">
                    <span class="number-mark">03</span>
                    <span class="icon">🌐</span>
                    <h3>泽尔通讯</h3>
                    <span class="sub">Zell Communications</span>
                    <p>构建透明、平等、去中心化的连接网络。让信息流动如自然生态循环，自由而有序。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 数据统计 ===== -->
    <div class="container">
        <section class="stats-section">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="number">12+</div>
                <div class="label">业务覆盖地区</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="number">200+</div>
                <div class="label">合作机构</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="number">4.8★</div>
                <div class="label">用户满意度</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="number">100%</div>
                <div class="label">碳中和目标</div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 新闻动态 ===== -->
    <div class="container">
        <section class="news-section" id="news">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>最新动态</h2>
                <span class="number">03</span>
            </div>
            <div class="news-grid">
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="date">2026.07.01</div>
                    <h4>星穹叙事创作者计划</h4>
                    <p>面向全球征集世界观设定与故事，构建开放的内容共创生态。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="date">2026.06.20</div>
                    <h4>概念产品 Eco-1 发布</h4>
                    <p>以可回收材料与模块化设计，探索电子产品的可持续未来。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="date">2026.06.05</div>
                    <h4>去中心化通讯协议达成</h4>
                    <p>推动构建更开放、安全的下一代信息网络基础设施。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 页脚 ===== -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-brand">
                    <h3>泽尔<span class="red">·</span>集团</h3>
                    <p>以自然之心，行科技之道。</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #555;">
                        © 2026 Zell Group. All rights reserved.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h4>业务</h4>
                    <a href="#">泽尔文化</a>
                    <a href="#">泽尔电子</a>
                    <a href="#">泽尔通讯</a>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h4>关于</h4>
                    <a href="#">理念</a>
                    <a href="#">团队</a>
                    <a href="#">合作</a>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h4>联系</h4>
                    <a href="mailto:zelculture@outlook.com">zelculture@outlook.com</a>
                    <a href="/gate.html">Gate 枢纽</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <span>上海 · 中国 · 2026</span>
            <span>
                <a href="/terms.html">法律声明</a>
                <a href="#">隐私政策</a>
                <a href="/">Arseeya 主站</a>
            </span>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>